{"tid":1380133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日全港司機 按！章！工！作！","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:04:14.000Z","uid":81805,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b4f2ae1a1f38fb80dbe636c98ee1fbe8abbdda","tid":1380133,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"港豬搭港鐵咁守規舉 咁鐘意衝入閘 <br />\n根據港鐵守則，要確保乘客安全，無遮住門先可以關門開車<br />\n有一乘客鼓燥 可能影響乘客安全 應該要報警處理 <br />\n<br />\n巴士司機最好就用最安全車速行 有乘客入少1毫子唔該叫佢落車<br />\n有人用優惠價格搭車 要求有關人士出示有關證明 <br />\n乘客企係黃線內 唔可以開車 好危險架 <br />\n<br />\n仲有咩大家可以補充"},{"pid":"e1d5a13d3e840cdd012450b690f24fd3dd0eb1da","tid":1380133,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"推手"},{"pid":"d00c29dc3cf1462b6b5fc5516e2a894bd3d088cc","tid":1380133,"uid":61521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca5a4cb054db95fdca91ea93ce4887e96a75af76","tid":1380133,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33ed3340339c77a5525e6b7e076f5aca37827fda","tid":1380133,"uid":81805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}